this law without delay and to revoke the immunity of the president of Al Zamalek, who insulted the whole country and slighted the one-hundred-million Egyptian population by claiming that Egypt is devoid of men, as seen in the video that has been trending on social media since yesterday, where he says that Egypt is 'a country that is full of sissies and faggots'\"."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔa.haː.na/"],"lanes_definition":null,"classical_definitions":null}